sentences: Runar Tafjord (born December 14, 1957 in Langev√•g, Norway) is a Norwegian French horn player, brother of the tubaist Stein Erik Tafjord, and uncle of the French horn player Hild Sofie Tafjord.

He has for many years played in various Scandinavian orchestras, including Oslo Filharmoniske Orkester, Den Norske Operas Orkester, Bergen Filharmoniske Orkester and 'Gothenburg Philharmonic Orchestra'.
In 2011 he received the "Statens arbeidsstipend" from the Norwegian government.
